@nicholaswatt Lessons from this; we need a strong army, a strong health provision and a strong industrial base.  The third rate of the last fifty plus years is no longer an option.  NHS procurement needs a kick up the backside.

@nicholaswatt Chris Whitty said the virus will be with us for a long time.  He has no evidence for this as for all we know it could all be but finished in the UK population and then it is a matter of rigorous control of borders.  Community testing needed urgently.
